data.description: Situated in a prime Denison subdivision, this three-bedroom, two-and-a-half-bath home awaits your pool party! Entertain friends with a splash in the 14'x28' PebbleTec finish gunite pool, heated and cooled, crafted in 2020 by Allison Pools. Enjoy 550 s.f. of pool deck! Additional relaxation space on the 14'x22' composite deck near the back patio. The family room, with a wood-burning fireplace, is ideal for hosting family events. Utilize the formal dining room for everyday or special occasions. The cozy breakfast nook offers pleasant views of the deck and pool. The primary bedroom suite is on the main floor, with two bedrooms, a second living area, and a full bath upstairs. Luxuries include a whole-house water softener, HVAC unit replacements, and water heater replacement in 2023. The fully irrigated yard enhances the property. Perfect for entertaining or unwinding, this home is a comfortable haven. No HOA! Priced at $480,000. Explore today!
